  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity and bring your card game vision to fruition with Card Engine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Design</strong>: The intuitive editor interface prioritizes user-friendliness, allowing you to start designing your first card in seconds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/da472ff2830df1a0cab1303b26f7b52d.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/da472ff2830df1a0cab1303b26f7b52d.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/da472ff2830df1a0cab1303b26f7b52d.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Asset Browser</strong>: The software includes a library with hundreds of built-in images. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/32b65656c61e251c073504ba4e669f78.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collection</strong>: Organize and manage your decks and cards with drag-and-drop functionality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/6b2f25ffe409d6849f43adad763844b6.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/6b2f25ffe409d6849f43adad763844b6.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/6b2f25ffe409d6849f43adad763844b6.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Templates</strong>: Create templates to speed up the card creation process. Changes made on a Template can be applied to all cards that derive from the template.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/9d27b41198a3656d013ded30885d8870.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/9d27b41198a3656d013ded30885d8870.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/9d27b41198a3656d013ded30885d8870.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Importer</strong>: Import your own images and fonts by simply dragging and dropping files into the asset browser, or through the native OS file browser.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/07f769bde59c23935928256d048cb075.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/07f769bde59c23935928256d048cb075.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/07f769bde59c23935928256d048cb075.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exporter</strong>: Export your cards as PNG, JPG, PDF or raw XML card data files with flexible settings and a real-time file preview. Cards automatically flow across pages (images) based on size and spacing. Choose from US or ISO paper standards for print, or export individual images with ease.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/f8bc705edf4bfd34ce204483a5db18b1.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/f8bc705edf4bfd34ce204483a5db18b1.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/f8bc705edf4bfd34ce204483a5db18b1.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And even more!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Project-based workflow</strong>: Create unique projects for various game ideas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flexible card size</strong>: Configure a custom card size for your project, or pick from common card standards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trash bin</strong>: Recently deleted cards can be recovered.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CSV</strong>: Export a CSV file of your project, then make  mass changes by editing and re-importing it. This can be used in conjunction with the Template system to produce new cards as well.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Examples</strong>: Import pre-made template cards made from the built in assets to quickly get you started.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Text icons</strong>: Insert icons into the text. Imported images can be added to the text icon widget.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variables</strong>: Create custom keys that formats to a custom value. E.g. {mana_legendary} as the key and 8 as the value that it will format to when rendered on a card. Variables supports text icons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Documentation</strong>: Get started guides, feature overviews, tips & tricks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discord community</strong>: Join the growing Discord community for both official and community support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessible data</strong>: The save data format is based on XML files, and they are fully editable.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card Engine is a project by a solo developer. You can reach out to me and share your opinions, ideas, and criticisms - I listen to your feedback.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity and bring your card game vision to fruition with Card Engine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Design</strong>: The intuitive editor interface prioritizes user-friendliness, allowing you to start designing your first card in seconds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/da472ff2830df1a0cab1303b26f7b52d.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/da472ff2830df1a0cab1303b26f7b52d.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/da472ff2830df1a0cab1303b26f7b52d.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Asset Browser</strong>: The software includes a library with hundreds of built-in images. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/32b65656c61e251c073504ba4e669f78.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collection</strong>: Organize and manage your decks and cards with drag-and-drop functionality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/6b2f25ffe409d6849f43adad763844b6.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/6b2f25ffe409d6849f43adad763844b6.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/6b2f25ffe409d6849f43adad763844b6.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Templates</strong>: Create templates to speed up the card creation process. Changes made on a Template can be applied to all cards that derive from the template.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/9d27b41198a3656d013ded30885d8870.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/9d27b41198a3656d013ded30885d8870.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/9d27b41198a3656d013ded30885d8870.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Importer</strong>: Import your own images and fonts by simply dragging and dropping files into the asset browser, or through the native OS file browser.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/07f769bde59c23935928256d048cb075.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/07f769bde59c23935928256d048cb075.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/07f769bde59c23935928256d048cb075.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exporter</strong>: Export your cards as PNG, JPG, PDF or raw XML card data files with flexible settings and a real-time file preview. Cards automatically flow across pages (images) based on size and spacing. Choose from US or ISO paper standards for print, or export individual images with ease.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/f8bc705edf4bfd34ce204483a5db18b1.poster.avif?t=1760396260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/f8bc705edf4bfd34ce204483a5db18b1.webm?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899310/extras/f8bc705edf4bfd34ce204483a5db18b1.mp4?t=1760396260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And even more!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Project-based workflow</strong>: Create unique projects for various game ideas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flexible card size</strong>: Configure a custom card size for your project, or pick from common card standards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trash bin</strong>: Recently deleted cards can be recovered.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CSV</strong>: Export a CSV file of your project, then make  mass changes by editing and re-importing it. This can be used in conjunction with the Template system to produce new cards as well.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Examples</strong>: Import pre-made template cards made from the built in assets to quickly get you started.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Text icons</strong>: Insert icons into the text. Imported images can be added to the text icon widget.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variables</strong>: Create custom keys that formats to a custom value. E.g. {mana_legendary} as the key and 8 as the value that it will format to when rendered on a card. Variables supports text icons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Documentation</strong>: Get started guides, feature overviews, tips & tricks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discord community</strong>: Join the growing Discord community for both official and community support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessible data</strong>: The save data format is based on XML files, and they are fully editable.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card Engine is a project by a solo developer. You can reach out to me and share your opinions, ideas, and criticisms - I listen to your feedback.</p>",
